author: vkumar
msg: Adding new functionalities in File server pipe-line
Now File server pipe-line can be configured from from jetspeed.properties, instead of portlet.xml
User can switch between File system or WEB-APP location to deliver. User can also deliver content from specific portlet application.
Developer just need to append there application name in url to serve content from there application
User can also server content from jetspeed. using the earlier url
